<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[الزَّخْرَفَةُ]</span>: زَخْرَفَ الشيءَ: إِذا زيَّنَهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ونبتٌ مُزَخْرَف.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
